<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Confirmation</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">

    <p>Dear <%= user.firstName %> <%= user.lastName %>,</p>

    <p>Thank you for registering with <%= appName %> . To confirm your registration, please click on the link below:</p>

    <p>
        <a href="<%= link %>">
            <%= link %>
        </a>
    </p>

    <p>
        (In case it does not work, you can copy and paste the above link in your browser's address bar)
    </p>

    <p>Once your registration is confirmed, please login to continue with the application.</p>

    <p>Best Wishes,<br>
        <%= appName %> 
    </p>

    <hr>

    <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #777;">
        You received this email because you are registered on <%= appName %>  with the email address: <%= user.email %>
    </p>

</body>
</html>
